Description: Rest on the Flight into Egypt; the Virgin sitting on the ground holding the infant Jesus, as two angels present her with flowers; next to them a donkey, grazing; St Joseph seated asleep, with two angels flying above; after Antonio Domenico Gabbiani. Etching with added mezzotint tone in black ink
Production date: 1766 (Date given in Calabi + De Vesme catalogue)
Bibliographic references: Calabi & De Vesme 1928 / Francesco Bartolozzi. Catalogue des estampes et notice biographique d'après les manuscrits de A. De Vesme entièrement réformés et complétés d'une étude critique par A. Calabi (90.II)
